ASTRA_DB_API_ENDPOINT=https://<your-database-endpoint>
ASTRA_DB_APPLICATION_TOKEN=<your-application-token>
```

Replace `<your-database-endpoint>` and `<your-application-token>` with your actual DataStax Astra DB credentials, I feel the disclaimer isn‚Äôt necessary, but hey ya never know. I am sure we've all done this once haha. This setup ensures that your application can securely connect to the Astra database and perform queries.

